data.description: Don't let this fantastic opportunity slip away! Enjoy a spacious fenced backyard. Prime location near Oceana Air Base, Redmill Commons, and the beautiful Sandbridge Beach. Benefit from the numerous amenities provided by the POA! Recent updates include new paint, flooring throughout, New oven and dishwasher complementing the fridge, Water Heater, Roof, and Siding, all with transferable warranties for the new owner. The seller's home warranty is also transferable to the buyer and seller will pay for 6 months of home warranty.  Book your showing now & don't miss out on this opportunity! Fire pit to convey! Seller willing to give Closing Cost Assistance with acceptable offer!
